Why is it that we would try to carve out time on our schedule, not only every other week

00:28:48.880 --> 00:28:54.840
as a church locally, but to have these guys travel in to be here with us and to set aside

00:28:54.840 --> 00:28:56.119
this time?

00:28:56.119 --> 00:28:57.599
I think God's pleased with it.

00:28:57.599 --> 00:29:01.960
I think it honors the Lord, and I'm thankful that we have an opportunity to do it.

00:29:01.960 --> 00:29:02.960
Let's pray together.

00:29:02.960 --> 00:29:04.280
Father, we love you.

00:29:04.280 --> 00:29:05.359
We thank you for loving us.

00:29:05.359 --> 00:29:08.359
We thank you for the privilege of being able to serve you.

00:29:08.359 --> 00:29:14.000
I thank you for Brother Hummel and, Lord, the vision that you gave him, the burden so

00:29:14.000 --> 00:29:20.479
many years ago to print and distribute your Word, sending the Word of God around the world.

00:29:20.479 --> 00:29:23.840
Lord, I thank you for their vision and for their ministry.

00:29:23.840 --> 00:29:29.200
I thank you for allowing our paths to cross so many years ago and allowing us as a local

00:29:29.200 --> 00:29:34.679
church to be able to be involved in this ministry and helping us to fulfill the responsibility

00:29:34.679 --> 00:29:38.520
that you've given us as a local church to reach the world with the gospel and this being

00:29:38.520 --> 00:29:44.080
one avenue, one opportunity to help us in fulfilling that responsibility.

00:29:44.080 --> 00:29:48.840
I thank you for the content of your Word, and, Lord, I think of all that I know about

00:29:48.840 --> 00:29:53.840
you and how I've learned it through your Word, and yes, the entrance of thy words giveth

00:29:53.840 --> 00:29:54.840
light.

00:29:54.840 --> 00:29:59.960
Lord, I pray that as we understand how precious this book is that we'd have a greater burden.

00:29:59.960 --> 00:30:04.240
in to desire that others would also have your word.

00:30:04.240 --> 00:30:10.000
God I thank you that our church family loves this ministry and participates in this ministry

00:30:10.000 --> 00:30:14.680
and I pray God that we would be faithful, Lord, that we would have the opportunity to

00:30:14.680 --> 00:30:21.440
give to help continue to provide the resources that are necessary to be able to provide these

00:30:21.440 --> 00:30:24.760
scriptures to these missionaries free of charge.

00:30:24.760 --> 00:30:29.400
I pray Lord that you'd help us to continue to have the strength to give of our time in

00:30:29.400 --> 00:30:31.400
order to be able to do the work.

00:30:31.400 --> 00:30:35.480
I pray that over these next couple of days, Lord, of ministry that you would be honored

00:30:35.480 --> 00:30:38.400
and glorified, that you'd help us to accomplish much.

00:30:38.400 --> 00:30:43.680
I pray the fellowship would be sweet, but God I pray that ultimately as we have an opportunity

00:30:43.680 --> 00:30:49.800
through this ministry to impact eternity, I pray that these scriptures as they're assembled

00:30:49.800 --> 00:30:53.800
and eventually distributed on the mission field, that souls would be saved and that

00:30:53.800 --> 00:30:58.800
lives would be changed and Lord I pray that you alone would be glorified.

00:30:58.800 --> 00:31:00.160
Well thank you for all that you'll do.

00:31:00.160 --> 00:31:01.920
We pray for the time of prayer.

00:31:01.920 --> 00:31:06.440
We thank you that we can have corporate prayer and Lord I thank you that you're a God who

00:31:06.440 --> 00:31:10.200
hears and answers prayer and I pray that you'd bless our time tonight.

00:31:10.200 --> 00:31:12.320
For it's in Christ's name we pray, amen.

00:31:12.320 --> 00:31:14.120
Does anyone need a prayer bulletin?

00:31:14.120 --> 00:31:14.560
You didn't get one.

